  "description": "Sir, I do apologize, but eleven corpus anchors of the Eldrazi brood was simply too many to leave un-anchored. Two BFZ-block defensive-side cards (Fortified Rampart, Encircling Fissure) depict the invasion directly; nine Modern Horizons 3 cards form the designer-coordinated Eldrazi-resurgence brief (Depth Defiler, Hope-Ender Coatl, Snapping Voidcraw, Idol of False Gods, Eldrazi Repurposer, Titans' Vanguard, Wastescape Battlemage, Twisted Riddlekeeper, Horrific Assault). The faction-collective precedent from phyrexia.md and endriders.md handles the character-layer modeling cleanly. The node also cross-references the new kor.md faction node as canonical BFZ-block adversary. I hope this helps, sir.",
